{
  "stem": "19596.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 429.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I knew that that night they couldn't get the dogs on me, because dogs can't smell in the wet weather.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They lose their smell in the rain.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Bavaria, it was snowing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "February, March.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'45.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I rolled down the hill, and then all of a sudden, I looked up and hell broke loose.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were counting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, before they go everywhere, they always keep on counting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when they finish counting, you can march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they counted and counted again, there was one missing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And hell broke loose.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And spotlights, dogs screaming, dogs running everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not down.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't go far, it was too steep for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see, I was trying to push myself up because I got hold up by plants.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I pushed myself away going to roll further.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was heading-- hiding under the leaves and lying there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then finally I saw the column marching, away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I started to get up, started to [? call, ?] started to walk as I could, stagger.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I went across.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And on a-- on-- on a hill, on a plateau, I came on the other side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I saw them again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "See what I did is they walked around, and I walked across.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I saw the whole column.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I ran quick back again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then I was in a forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The next day, I was starving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was trying to get a rabbit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyhow, I went up a tree.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then I went up the tree, and I slept there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In a tree, I tied myself up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Oh, in the meantime, I found a dead Russian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "A dead Russian prisoner with-- with-- with a paint in the back, with a head in the river.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
